Martyn Keith https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martyn_Keith 0 Martyn Keith was an Australian actor, writer and director who worked during the silent era. In 1912 he worked as an acting teacher in Lismore, New South Wales where he also performed in plays for his own company.
